java.lang.Object

public class GssPropertyManager
extends java.lang.Object

Single point of entry to register all GssElements types and Properties Useful for auto-generating JavaDoc and auto-extending Batik as well as processing syntactic sugar CSS into real CSS (e.g. 'line-thickness' -> 'border-width')
